 These mosquitos 'fly' from nearby cells with the distribution of the distance
 and concentration of the source cells determined by model parameters.
 Each mosquito is assumed to 'bite' an individual with HbAS/SS or HbAA genotype
 according to the cell's frequency and, as before, each infection 'succeeds'
 with probabilty dependent on its 
